Bumps <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop|rubocop> from 1.56.4 to 1.57.0.

Release notes

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/releases|rubocop's releases>._

> *RuboCop 1.57*
> *New features*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12227|#12227>: Add new `Style/SingleLineDoEndBlock` cop. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12246|#12246>: Make `Lint/RedundantSafeNavigation` aware of constant receiver. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12257|#12257>: Make `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` aware of `merge` methods. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> 
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12244|#12244>: Fix a false negative for `Lint/Debugger` when using debugger method inside block. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12231|#12231>: Fix a false negative for `Metrics/ModuleLength` when defining a singleton class in a module. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12249|#12249>: Fix a false positive `Style/IdenticalConditionalBranches` when `if`..`else` with identical leading lines and assign to condition value. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12253|#12253>: Fix `Lint/LiteralInInterpolation` to accept an empty string literal interpolated in words literal. (<https://github.com/knu|`@​knu`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12198|#12198>: Fix an error for flip-flop with beginless or endless ranges. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12259|#12259>: Fix an error for `Lint/MixedCaseRange` when using nested character class in regexp. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12237|#12237>: Fix an error for `Style/NestedTernaryOperator` when a ternary operator has a nested ternary operator within an `if`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12228|#12228>: Fix false negatives for `Style/MultilineBlockChain` when using multiline block chain with safe navigation operator. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12247|#12247>: Fix false negatives for `Style/RedundantParentheses` when using logical or comparison expressions with redundant parentheses. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12226|#12226>: Fix false positives for `Layout/MultilineMethodCallIndentation` when aligning methods in multiline block chain. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12076|#12076>: Fixed an issue where the top-level cache folder was named differently during two consecutive rubocop runs. (<https://github.com/K-S-A|`@​K-S-A`>)
> 
> *Changes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12235|#12235>: Enable auto parallel inspection when config file is specified. (<https://github.com/aboutNisblee|`@​aboutNisblee`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12234|#12234>: Enhance `Style/FormatString`'s autocorrection when using known conversion methods whose return value is not an array. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12128|#12128>: Make `Style/GuardClause` aware of `define_method`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12126|#12126>: Make `Style/RedundantFilterChain` aware of `select.present?` when `ActiveSupportExtensionsEnabled` config is `true`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12250|#12250>: Mark `Lint/RedundantRequireStatement` as unsafe autocorrect. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12097|#12097>: Mark unsafe autocorrect for `Style/ClassEqualityComparison`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12210|#12210>: Mark `Style/RedundantFilterChain` as unsafe autocorrect. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
